                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-blue-500/30 text-blue-300">
                    Tank
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">
              Heavy-armored melee powerhouses wielding massive two-handed swords. Warriors build Kinetic Energy
              through attacks and unleash devastating Kinetic abilities. They excel at cleaving through enemies
              and can absorb tremendous damage when tanking.
            </p>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/50">
              <strong class="text-white/70">Resource:</strong> Kinetic Energy
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
<!-- Spellslinger -->
        <div class="card-gaming overflow-hidden">
          <div
            class="p-6 border-b border-white/10"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2), transparent);"
