                <div class="flex gap-2 mt-1">
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-red-500/30 text-red-300">DPS</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-green-500/30 text-green-300">
                    Healer
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">
              Dual-pistol wielding gunslingers who blend magic with marksmanship. Spellslingers use Spell Surge
              to empower their abilities, trading sustained damage for powerful burst windows. They're mobile
              and deadly, with strong support healing capabilities.
            </p>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/50">
              <strong class="text-white/70">Resource:</strong> Spell Power + Spell Surge
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
<!-- Stalker -->
        <div class="card-gaming overflow-hidden">
          <div
            class="p-6 border-b border-white/10"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2), transparent);"
