            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">
              Stealthy assassins with nano-enhanced claws. Stalkers use Suit Power for their abilities and
              can enter stealth for devastating opener attacks. They're highly mobile and can evasion-tank
              through deflection and self-healing.
            </p>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/50">
              <strong class="text-white/70">Resource:</strong> Suit Power
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
<!-- Engineer -->
        <div class="card-gaming overflow-hidden">
